OL,6,FA rail construction worker who
OL,7,Fdefrauded at least #27,000 using fake
OL,8,Ftrain tickets is due to be sentenced.
OL,10,FRory Stickels was commuting from his
OL,11,FKent home to North London.
OL,13,FHe was caught after a suspicious staff
OL,14,Fmember at St Pancras railway station
OL,15,Fnoticed his expired ticket, and then
OL,16,Fdiscovered nine other forgeries in his
OL,17,Fwallet in January last year.
