OL,6,FThe 45-year-old construction worker,
OL,7,Fof Queens Road, Romney, was employed
OL,8,Ffor Network Rail through an agency
OL,9,Fwhile he was living in Kent, and had
OL,10,F"fallen on hard times", according to
OL,11,Fprosecutor Zahid Hussain at Highbury
OL,12,FMagistrates.
