OL,4,C#27,000 using fake train tickets
OL,6,F"Because of the expense incurred, he
OL,7,Fmade a foolish decision to use what he
OL,8,Fdescribed as a fraudulent forged
OL,9,Fticket to commute to and from home
OL,10,Finto London, from London back home,"
OL,11,Fsaid Mr Hussain, explaining how a
OL,12,F"discrepancy" was found on an out of
OL,13,Fdate ticket, which then led a rail
OL,14,Fworker to find nine more fakes, dating
OL,15,Fback to 2019, inside the builder's
OL,16,Fwallet.
