OL,6,FMr Hussain said Stickels was supplied
OL,7,Fby "a third party" every time his fake
OL,8,Fticket expired until he was caught and
OL,9,Fhanded over to British Transport
OL,10,FPolice.
OL,12,FThe cost of a real season ticket, from
OL,13,FAshford International to St Pancras,
OL,14,Franges from between #6,000 to #9,000
OL,15,Ffor high-speed services.JThe estimated
OL,16,Ffinancial cost was between #27,000 to
OL,17,F#66,000.
