OL,6,FA probation officer told the court
OL,7,FStickels had appeared "upset and
OL,8,Ftearful" throughout his probation
OL,9,Finterview.
OL,11,F"It was during the time he was
OL,12,Flamenting the difficulty of his daily
OL,13,Fdrive that someone offered him the
OL,14,Ftickets at a discounted rate. He told
OL,15,Fme he paid them around #1,000 a year.
OL,16,FHe told me he was aware they were not
OL,17,F100 per cent legitimate, but he did
OL,18,Fnot know they were forged," said the
OL,19,Fprobation officer.
