OL,6,FStickels lost his railway job but has
OL,7,Fsince regained a construction job. The
OL,8,Fprobation worker also said "he regrets
OL,9,Fhis actions" and now understands the
OL,10,Fimpact of the fraud on the train
OL,11,Fcompany and the effect it has on
OL,12,Fticket prices.
OL,14,FStickels was released on unconditional
OL,15,Fbail ahead of sentencing at Inner
OL,16,FLondon Crown Court at a later date.
